<% var epdqParams = epdqResponse.parameters(); -%>
<p class="summary">You have completed your payment to the Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office (FCO).</p>

<p>You have paid for <%= pluralise("death registration", registrationCount(epdqParams)) %> and <%= pluralise("certificate", documentCount(epdqParams)) %><% if (epdqParams['postage'] == 'yes'){ %>, plus postage<% } -%>.</p>

<p>Your online payment reference is <%= epdqParams['payid'] %>. You must:</p>

<ul>
  <li>write the payment reference on your application form</li>
  <li>print out this page and include it with your application</li>
</ul>

<p>If you’re in the UK then send your application form and documents to:</p>

<div class="address">
  <div class="adr org fn">
    <p>
      Overseas Registration Unit<br/>
      Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office<br/>
      PO Box 6255<br/>
      Milton Keynes<br/>
      MK10 1XX
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<p>If you’re abroad then send your application form and documents to:</p>

